《'''暴力小姐'''》（''Miss Violence''）是一部2013年[[亚历桑德罗·阿万纳斯|亚历桑德罗·阿万纳斯]]执导的希腊电影，获得[[第70届威尼斯影展|第70届威尼斯影展]]最佳导演和最佳男演员（Themis Panou）两个奖<ref name="Venice">{{cite web |url=http://www.labiennale.org/en/cinema/70th-festival/line-up/off-sel/venezia70 |title=Venezia 70 |accessdate=2013-07-26 |work=labiennale |archive-date=2013-07-28 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20130728070816/http://www.labiennale.org/en/cinema/70th-festival/line-up/off-sel/venezia70 |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref name="Guardian">{{cite web |url=http://www.guardian.co.uk/film/2013/jul/25/venice-film-festival-2013-line-up/ |title=Venice film festival 2013: the full line-up |accessdate=2013-07-26 |work=The Guardian |archive-date=2013-07-25 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20130725191906/http://www.guardian.co.uk/film/2013/jul/25/venice-film-festival-2013-line-up |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{cite news|title=Vince l'Italia: Leone d'oro a "Sacro GRA"|url=http://www.repubblica.it/speciali/cinema/venezia/edizione2013/2013/09/07/news/venezia_vincitore-66075620/?ref=HRER3-1|accessdate=7 September 2013|newspaper=La Repubblica|date=7 September 2013|archive-date=2013-09-08|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20130908014725/http://www.repubblica.it/speciali/cinema/venezia/edizione2013/2013/09/07/news/venezia_vincitore-66075620/?ref=HRER3-1|dead-url=no}}</ref>。导演表示本片初衷源自[[歐債危機|希腊经济危机]]，片中故事取材真实，调查一年多才开机。

== 剧情 ==
故事围绕一个普通而又处处透着蹊跷的希腊中产家庭展开，通过家中女孩儿安其利奇在自己11岁的[[生日|生日]]派对上跳楼[[自杀|自杀]]，引出了这个家庭不为人知的暴力和丑恶。

